  Title: The Complete Works of Chuang Tzu
  Translator: Burton Watson
Title: The Sign Of Virtue Complete
---
Tzu-ch'an said, "You, a man like this - and still you claim to be
better than a Yao! Take a look at your virtue and see if it's not
enough to give you cause to reflect!"
